This is to build linaro debian buster rootfs for following SBC's:
rpi4b  ( Raspberry Pi 4B )
radxa  ( Rock Pi 4B plus )
rk3328 ( Renegade ROC-RK3328-CC )
tinker ( ASUS TinkerBoard )

Steps to build rootfs:

1. git clone https://github.com/chenphilip888/build-rootfs-4SBCs.git
   cd build-rootfs-4SBCs

2. Install live-build:
   sudo apt-get install debootstrap debhelper kpartx gdisk devscripts dh-systemd live-build isolinux po4a

3. cd ~/build-rootfs-4SBCs/rpi4b
   make all
   The result is in ~/build-rootfs-4SBCs/rpi4b/linaro-rootfs.img
   make clean

4. cd ~/build-rootfs-4SBCs/radxa
   make all
   The result is in ~/build-rootfs-4SBCs/radxa/linaro-rootfs.img
   make clean

5. cd ~/build-rootfs-4SBCs/rk3328
   make all
   The result is in ~/build-rootfs-4SBCs/rk3328/linaro-rootfs.img
   make clean

6. cd ~/build-rootfs-4SBCs/tinker
   make all
   The result is in ~/build-rootfs-4SBCs/tinker/linaro-rootfs.img
   make clean

